<%= notice_paragraph "Thank you for applying to offer group health coverage through #{Settings.site.short_name}.  However, based on our eligibility criteria we are not able to offer group health coverage in #{Settings.site.short_name} for your employees at this time." %>

<%= notice_paragraph "At this time, you will not be able to offer coverage to your employees through #{Settings.site.short_name}.  If you would like to re-structure your benefit offering to encourage more employees to participate, you may do so by creating a new open enrollment period."%>

<%= notice_paragraph "In addition, there is a special annual enrollment period at the end of each year during which employers can offer group health coverage effective January 1st without having a minimum level of employee enrollment."%>

